{"tid":2445934,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「讓公司再偉大」特朗普雕塑熱賣","createTime":"2021-03-14T04:52:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T04:52:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f741249318f49ecfdaa1684a2b679fa885ea2c4c","tid":2445934,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T04:52:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210313/SVWPDWFYTNHDZHY647KFEUPSHE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210313%2FSVWPDWFYTNHDZHY647KFEUPSHE%2F&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfNTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=da90158c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210313%2FSVWPDWFYTNHDZHY647KFEUPSHE%2F&h=223d9f6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210313/SVWPDWFYTNHDZHY647KFEUPSHE/</a><br />\n<br />\n「讓公司再偉大」特朗普雕塑熱賣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Fr9_L5lqJnx9s4JcaH0DCN9ZuTc=/1984x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZHR33TWFUVBPXCNTLEMB62GRHA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFr9_L5lqJnx9s4JcaH0DCN9ZuTc%3D%2F1984x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZHR33TWFUVBPXCNTLEMB62GRHA.jpg&h=97af0e88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■淘寶有售的特朗普外形「西天懂佛」禪修雕塑。<br />\n<br />\n內地淘寶網有人出售自家設計的美國前總統特朗普的雕塑，名為「西天懂佛」，引發外界關注。有網友笑稱，放在公司當擺設可「讓你的公司再度偉大」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最貴賣4,778元<br />\n<br />\n這個特朗普的雕塑一般售價999元人民幣（約1,194港元）。製作雕塑的是福建廈門一間公司，淘寶網上的描述稱，這個以白瓷製成的特朗普雕像，盤腿席地而坐，呈現打坐姿態，一片祥和。《環球時報》訪問雕塑創作者，他表示.........................<br />\n<br />\n《環球時報》"}]}